m cells", "obj": "cell_type", "prob": 0.8662681579589844, "span": {"begin": 3734, "end": 3744}}, {"id": ["CUI-less"], "is_neural_normalized": false, "mention": "Naked oocytes", "obj": "cell_type", "prob": 0.875508189201355, "span": {"begin": 3794, "end": 3807}}, {"id": ["NCBITaxon:9838"], "is_neural_normalized": false, "mention": "Camel", "obj": "species", "prob": 0.9651588797569275, "span": {"begin": 3828, "end": 3833}}, {"id": ["mesh:D014212"], "is_neural_normalized": false, "mention": "ATRA", "obj": "drug", "prob": 0.9883954524993896, "span": {"begin": 3845, "end": 3849}}, {"id": ["CL:0000023"], "is_neural_normalized": false, "mention": "oocyte", "obj": "cell_type", "prob": 0.8815180063247681, "span": {"begin": 3932, "end": 3938}}, {"id": ["NCBITaxon:9031"], "is_neural_normalized": false, "mention": "Chicken", "obj": "species", "prob": 0.9103420376777649, "span": {"begin": 4037, "end": 4044}}, {"id": ["mesh:D014212"], "is_neural_normalized": false, "mention": "ATRA", "obj": "drug", "prob": 0.8025444746017456, "span": {"begin": 4056, "end": 4060}}], "text": "Animal models               Model            Relevant observations            Reference                  Vitamin A deficient (VAD) rats            Oocytes fail to enter meiosis in ovaries of VAT rats due to atAR deficiency.&nbsp;      Meiotic entry measured by SYCP3 expression was detected in 10% and 30% of germ cells in rats fed severely deficient (1.5ug of atRA per gram of diet) and moderately deficient (12ug of atRA per gram of diet) atRA diets, respectively, whilst controls had 70% of germ cells enter meiosis.      The expression of the atRA-responsive gene, Stra8, was reduced by approximately 90% and 50% in the severely and moderately atRA-deficient ovaries, respectively, compared with the atRA-sufficient controls.            (Li &amp; Clagett-Dame, 2009)            &nbsp;  In vitro/ex vivo               Study type            Species            Compound            Effect Dose            Duration            Results            Reference                  Fetal ovaries in culture            Mouse             WIN 18,446     (ALDH1A2 inhibitor)            2 &micro;M            3-12 d            Reduced Stra8 expression and germ cell loss.            (Rosario et al, 2020)                  Fetal ovaries in culture            Mouse             BMS-189453 (RAR antagonist)            1 &micro;M            3 d            Reduced STRA8-positve germ cells without overall oocyte loss            (Minkina et al, 2017)                  Embryonic stem cells            Mouse            ATRA            100 nM            &nbsp;            Activates meiosis-related gene network            (Aoki &amp; Takada, 2012)                  Embryonic stem cells            Mouse            BMS-493 (RAR antagonist)            10 &micro;M            &nbsp;            Inhibition of expression meiosis-related genes            (Aoki &amp; Takada, 2012)                  Naked oocytes, matured            Mouse            ATRA            2 &micro;M            24 h            Culture in presence of atRA increased meiosis resumption and formation of metaphase II oocytes            (Tahaei et al, 2011)                  fetal ovaries in culture            Human            ATRA            1 &micro;M            1-3 d            atRA strongly promote initiation of germ cell meiosis            (le Bouffant et al, 2010)                  fetal ovaries in culture            Human            BMS-189453 (RAR antagonist)            10 &micro;M            14 d            Partial inhibition of meiotic entry of germ cells            (le Bouffant et al, 2010)                  fetal ovaries in culture            Human            Citral            55 &micro;M            14 d            Partial inhibition of meiotic entry of germ cells by inhibiting RA synthesizing enzymes            (le Bouffant et al, 2010)                  Fetal ovaries in culture            Mouse            AGN193109 (RAR antagonist)            5 &micro;M            48 h or 72 h            Meiotic program inhibited            (Bowles et al, 2006)                  Fetal ovaries in culture            Mouse            BMS-204493 (RAR antagonist)            5 &micro;M            2 d            Stra8 expression not upregulated in germ cells, marker for failed initiation of meiosis            (Koubova et al, 2006)                  Fetal ovaries in culture            Mouse            ATRA            1 &micro;M            &nbsp;            Acceleration of germ cells into meiosis, reduction in total number of germ cells            (Livera et al, 2000)                  Fetal ovaries in culture            Mouse            CD0336 (RAR&alpha; agonist)            1 nM            &nbsp;            Acceleration of germ cells into meiosis, reduction in total number of germ cells            (Livera et al, 2000)                  Naked oocytes, matured            Camel            ATRA            20 &micro;M            24 h            Stimulates meiosis and promotes oocyte viability            (Saddeldin et al, 2019)                  Fetal ovaries in culture            Chicken            ATRA            1 &micro;M            &nbsp;            Stimulates meiotic initiation.&nbsp;             (Yu et al, 2013)            &nbsp;", "timestamp": "Mon Jun 08 15:35:17 +0000 2026"}